summary:
There once was a girl named Sindiwe Magona.&#13;
She had a special gift for stories. At night, little Sindiwe’s grandmother told her magical stories about ogres and giants, animals of the forests, and the little creatures of the veld. This was Sindiwe’s favourite time.&#13;
See how she grows up to live out her own adventures as she travels over oceans to change the world with her stories.&#13;
